The convert command allows you to make a player a guild member.
The syntax for the command is 'Convert <player_name>'.
The player has to be present, and meet all the requirements of
the guild, including the 5th level requirement and the alignment
requirement.  Mitra is very generous to members who perform
a conversion.  Caution if you convert unwilling players, Mitra
can also be very harsh!
 
